txt.en: You have become a proficient Journeyman Jeweller! You may now use Expert Jeweller recipes, or continue to work towards Journeyman Jeweller mastery.\n\nAdditionally, you are now eligible to join the <rgb=#00FF00>Jeweller's Guild</rgb>, a special reputation faction open only to Expert Jewellers. To join the Jeweller's Guild, seek out a Master or Mistress of Crafting Guild
